Nitisha has been formerly trained under Guru Hare Krishna Behera. She has been dancing for the past 17 years now. She has travelled around India to various places like Mumbai, Jodhpur, Hyderabad, Goa, to name a few, for various shows and also to Cairo, Egypt for the Nile Festival. Belly Dance  Drum solo Like in Indian classical dance, there are multiple pieces that are performed and learnt, in a belly dance repertoire, the Drum Solo is something which falls in the latter half. This drum solo, being performed today, is a combination of various rhythms likeBalaedi, Saidi, Khaleeji, Felahi and Ayub belonging to both Egypt and the Gulf. All these folk rhythms have been adapted in Raqs Sharqi stylization of dance, that is the classical Egyptian style. Music is by Mario Kirlis.

UURZ0_wuPDo.keywords: Mountain bike mtb Diamondback full suspension hard tail wreck run over truck damage repair expensiveMy mountain bike after fateful meeting with truck aka "I will let the bike shop determine that".This is my Diamondback full suspension mountain bike. It is not the best bike out there, but it suits me just fine for now. Yesterday October 7, 2010 it got ran over by a truck while on a bike path. The fellow has agreed to pay the repair costs, which right now stand at 265. The bike was purchased brand new for about 700. This is the video I took of my bike before I brought it to one of the local bike repair shops to document the damage should the fellow decide not to follow up on his word. When he ran over my bike, he smashed the back end, and stayed on it, which dug the whole bike into the ground. If your bike gets run over, or you have a bad wreck on it take it in for repairs. Some types of damage to bikes... especially frame and rimhub damage can cause fatal accidents down the road. Its not worth saving a few hundred on repairs only to have a very serious and probably even MORE expensive mishap down the road. Its fun to live on the edge, but it's more fun to be alive to do such things!
